title.rendered: THG Spoiler Report: A One Tree Hill Wedding and More

content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

It will be a quiet couple weeks across the television dial through January 1.

But once the calendar flips to 2011, viewers can look forward to weddings, murder mysteries and a lot more. Follow the links below, courtesy of our friends at TV Fanatic, but a glance at what’s ahead on various shows…

One Tree Hill spoilers: This CW drama will pay homage to The Hangover, as Brooke has a bit too much fun at her bachelorette party.

Pretty Little Liars spoilers: A will apologize to Hanna when this ABC Family hit returns. But she’ll do it in a mysterious, creepy manner.

The Vampire Diaries spoilers: Michael Trevino says we can trust Jules and her intentions with Tyler.

Desperate Housewives spoilers: Who shot Paul Young? That’s the question viewers will be asking for the next several weeks.

Fringe spoilers: Yes, this show is moving to Friday. No, it swears, this isn’t a death sentence.
